name: Homeprototype
tagline: Software for a hosting website "homeprototype.org" to host user -submited designs for people to print on home 3D printers.
body:
Software for a hosting website "[homeprototype.org](http://homeprototype.org/)" to host user -submited designs for people to print on home 3D printers.

Please join as a contributor if you are interested to help and help us in brainstorming in the wiki! (So coding can begin ASAP.)

See [The Wiki](https://github.com/MarcusWolschon/homeprototype/wiki) for details.
